splay Settings</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-10.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-10.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Events List Widget\"></a><p>Events List Widget</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-11.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-11.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Mobile Month View\"></a><p>Mobile Month View</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-12.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-12.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"CSV Importer\"></a><p>CSV Importer</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:15186:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">no support for issues</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ohiowebpro\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d5801f2388436045c0e0316ec357d53?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d5801f2388436045c0e0316ec357d53?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ohiowebpro\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ohiowebpro</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 5, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have the pro version of this software and support seems to not care. In calendar view, after you switch months, you cannot click the view all link within a day. Notified support months ago, and they admitted it was an issue with the plugin and that it would be fixed in the next version. Only that never happened. Still broken months later. They have been no help for a temporary solution. They are only focused on rolling out the next version of features, and not fixing bugs. I would stay away from anything by Modern Tribe.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good plugin with correct server settings...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/screenload\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc70ad2781cf47fc61c296d3cfbc5d05?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc70ad2781cf47fc61c296d3cfbc5d05?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/screenload\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Screenload <small>(screenload)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 10, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin causes me nothing but trouble.\n\n<del datetime=\"2019-12-10T12:55:38+00:00\">Errors, wrong URLs,</del> shortcodes not working like intended...\n\n<del datetime=\"2019-12-10T12:55:38+00:00\">And today we had some angry guests because the TIME is displayed one hour off.</del>\n\n<del datetime=\"2019-12-10T12:55:38+00:00\">10 am inside WordPress backend, 9 am displayed on the front end. I mean.. wtf?</del></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">..simply Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cirowordpress\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7f860170ca6740d7f99fe767c924c89e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7f860170ca6740d7f99fe767c924c89e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cirowordpress\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cirowp <small>(cirowordpress)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Well done...clean ...easy to use anche powerfull at the same time. Great plugin, in my opinion the best events calendar!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Bullet Proof</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mongrel\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c3e13f9d247a89f9e310d7235b6b0ae?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c3e13f9d247a89f9e310d7235b6b0ae?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mongrel\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mongrel</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">What can I say? It\'s the one that works. Every time.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Terrible soporte en su versin de Ticket Plus</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joelramirezleal\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dce08a2c7b602e51b0c73ddd48410556?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dce08a2c7b602e51b0c73ddd48410556?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joelramirezleal\" class=\"reviewer-name\">joelramirezleal</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 21, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">No lo recomendara si no existe alguna otra alternativa, el soporte hasta el momento es terrible. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works great!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/terryflhamilton\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/44d729f4e5fe4d1cd0d3b15f62160a47?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/44d729f4e5fe4d1cd0d3b15f62160a47?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/terryflhamilton\" class=\"reviewer-name\">terryflhamilton</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 18, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Just what I was looking for! Thank you!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">amazing plugin TERRIBLE SUPPORT !!!!!!!!!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/urishahaff\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5da2e7f2f7dd2bc2aca0b4853a0d6055?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5da2e7f2f7dd2bc2aca0b4853a0d6055?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/urishahaff\" class=\"reviewer-name\">urishahaff</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">i had a problem that all my dates showed in the edit event view the same start and end date - regardless of the real date of the event which was stored correctly.\nJamie from the support told me irrelevant stuff- clear your cache. flush permalinks, switch template - while the problem obviously was the display of time.\nwhen i went to the display settings - for some reason the display of a month and day view was incorrect and set to 2F - thatws why all the dates showed the same day.\nsuch an easy and simple solution and should be the first thing to check if she had just listened to the problem. \ni had spent 3 days of conversations - and felt so hopeless. when you buy a plugin - you want real tech support and not some high school kids that repeats banal stuff like flush your cache. \nthe plugin is great and highly recommended but the support I\'ve experienced was just terrible!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\nthank god i resolved it - i think it\'s a waste of time to pay for their support in the future. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good, but no RSVP ability</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/livingcminca\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7da803dff35caeb532e5f3d401f45a5a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7da803dff35caeb532e5f3d401f45a5a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/livingcminca\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Naomi <small>(livingcminca)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 13, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great plugin to just create and list events, unfortunately, there\'s no RSVP functionality on the unpaid version of this plugin as far as I can tell so it lacks some options I would have liked. \n </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/juliettdou\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cb2f394b42089f2bddec4a26f62525f2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cb2f394b42089f2bddec4a26f62525f2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/juliettdou\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Juliette Douffet <small>(juliettdou)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 10, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Best in the category. Has a lot of community behind and it\'s easy to find or extend its features.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple enough even in Free version</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n