on <span class=\"review-date\">December 6, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using this plugin for a long time and it is great. Set it and forget it for the most part. Updates always seem to go well. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/comargonzalez73\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/39cf848787fd1b2321344d6482acec9e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/39cf848787fd1b2321344d6482acec9e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/comargonzalez73\" class=\"reviewer-name\">comargonzalez73</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 3, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Easy to understand.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simplest and best plugin in the whole directory</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/spwebguy\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f7ec0c68ec3bc12a74e6c0c4a82b2ae9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f7ec0c68ec3bc12a74e6c0c4a82b2ae9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/spwebguy\" class=\"reviewer-name\">WP Darko <small>(spwebguy)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This thing is the best plugin you\'ll ever have on a WordPress site.\n\nThis should be a default plugin for building forms. Don\'t let WP Forms and other competitors take your users.\n\nYou are the first, and the best.\n\nThank you. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent plugin.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bennylegolas89\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d7f61a1ba291410dd92056657ff41546?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d7f61a1ba291410dd92056657ff41546?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bennylegolas89\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bennylegolas89</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Look no further...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kylerboudreau\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b832ab7f2fcc8ae913c7d80e183ffcc9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b832ab7f2fcc8ae913c7d80e183ffcc9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kylerboudreau\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kylerboudreau</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 29, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using Contact Form 7 for around 5 years. I\'ve installed it on over 100 WordPress sites. This is the best one out there. Yes, the interface isn\'t drag and drop, but that\'s actually ideal -- You have full control over the styling and layout of your forms. Highly recommended!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good one with potential</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/paulcityhopper\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/63f3809f79c70238ac04fd5ffbc3c4dd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/63f3809f79c70238ac04fd5ffbc3c4dd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/paulcityhopper\" class=\"reviewer-name\">PaulCityhopper</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 27, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is a really good plugin. Buuuuut...\n\n1. There should be an Redirection integrated!\n2. Mails are marked as Spam, I dont know if the Plugin is the reason!?\n3. It would be great if there is another integrated Spam Protection as reCaptcha. The reCAPTCHA Badge is annoying.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin Thank you</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/leogo\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5f83929cf25f49e1625725af8df82eb5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5f83929cf25f49e1625725af8df82eb5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/leogo\" class=\"reviewer-name\">leogo</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 25, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you Contact form 7 developers for developing such a great plugin for creating Wordpress Forms.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple and powerful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gmulakwp\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/106fe2a753e6bb8d4589fe8a42fa213d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/106fe2a753e6bb8d4589fe8a42fa213d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gmulakwp\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gmulakwp</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 23, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Wow, what a nice plugin!  1.  Modify a form,  2.  Add a page, 3.  Plug the form header into it.  4.  Make a link to it.  \n\nGood coding is simply elegant, and this is.  \n\nGreat job, thank you!  \nGeorge Mulak, KM6AFI</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Time to find another Contact Forum Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jw555\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5110c385c6c0e0f0e85104a1dc3e1b04?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5110c385c6c0e0f0e85104a1dc3e1b04?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jw555\" class=\"reviewer-name\">JW555</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have always trusted Contact Form 7, however, over the last few years I have found my sites were using the contact form to send automated spam.  \n\nI have tried using three different methods to stop this, including Quiz, tick boxes and captcha, despite this the hackers seem to be able to read and bypass the code on this plugin sending a plethora of spam messages.\n\nThe worst thing is that the messages go to my server and my ISP rightly spots that they are spam but then it puts MY DOMAIN on the spam block list.\n\nThe contact form 7 plugin has not had any real upgrade of functionality for years and has fallen behind.\n\nSo sadly I must now try to find another Contact form plugin</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.5.1.6.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:1:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"screenshot-1.png\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:7:\"contact\";s:7:\"contact\";s:12:\"contact-form\";s:12:\"contact form\";s:5:\"email\";s:5:\"email\";s:8:\"feedback\";s:8:\"feedback\";s:4:\"form\";s:4:\"form\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:139:{s:3:\"1.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.1.zip\";s:4:\"1.10\";s:62:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.0.1\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.0.1.zip\";s:6:\"1.10.1\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.1.zip\";s:3:\"1.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.2.zip\";s:3:\"1.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.1\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.2\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.2.zip\";s:3:\"1.4\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.1\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.2\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin